hardwired relationship

00:04:28.900 --> 00:04:31.260
between the thinking areas
of the brain

00:04:31.260 --> 00:04:33.360
and the feeling areas
of the brain.

00:04:33.360 --> 00:04:36.430
One affects the other
at all times.

00:04:40.830 --> 00:04:45.600
MAN:
It is not possible to have a
properly working reason system

00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:49.330
without having a properly
working emotion system.

00:04:49.330 --> 00:04:53.700
What you think, what you create,
the problems you solve,

00:04:53.700 --> 00:04:57.060
the way you reason
don't exist in a vacuum.

00:04:57.060 --> 00:05:01.830
There is always a backdrop
of emotion and feeling.

00:05:01.830 --> 00:05:04.460
We are not thinking machines.

00:05:04.460 --> 00:05:07.600
We are feeling machines
that think.

