00:12:39.930 --> 00:12:42.230
NARRATOR:
Marvin has trouble deciding,

00:12:42.230 --> 00:12:45.000
because he has lost
the emotional connection

00:12:45.000 --> 00:12:46.560
to his past.

00:12:46.560 --> 00:12:50.230
Memories and the emotions
that go with them

00:12:50.230 --> 00:12:52.430
guide our every decision.

00:12:52.430 --> 00:12:56.500
But for Marvin,
memories are bereft of feeling.

00:12:58.500 --> 00:13:01.260
DAMASIO:
All the things
that you go through in your life

00:13:01.260 --> 00:13:05.400
in terms of decisions
are inevitably accompanied

00:13:05.400 --> 00:13:09.360
by some kind of emotion,
positive or negative.

00:13:14.530 --> 00:13:18.560
Each decision has some kind
of similarity

00:13:18.560 --> 00:13:21.430
with a decision of the past.

00:13:21.430 --> 00:13:27.100
And when you are in a position
to decide once again,

00:13:27.100 --> 00:13:29.560
you will call up
an emotional memory

00:13:29.560 --> 00:13:32.530
that will appear
as a gut feeling

00:13:32.530 --> 00:13:36.760
and will lead you
in one direction or another.

00:13:36.760 --> 00:13:40.660
So what you have
is literally a navigational aid,

00:13:40.660 --> 00:13:44.760
something that helps you get
to the right decision.

00:13:46.430 --> 00:13:48.230
And if that is broken down,

00:13:48.230 --> 00:13:51.030
then you're at the mercy
of facts and logic

00:13:51.030 --> 00:13:53.200
and that's just not good enough.

00:13:55.200 --> 00:13:59.600
NARRATOR:
Marvin is rudderless as he
navigates through daily life.

00:14:02.760 --> 00:14:07.630
But, um, I'm not an invalid.

00:14:07.630 --> 00:14:09.930
I'm not, uh, I'm not...

00:14:09.930 --> 00:14:13.460
Some days people
probably think I am

00:14:13.460 --> 00:14:15.500
but I'm not.

00:14:15.500 --> 00:14:19.560
You know, I'm able
to do a lot of things.

00:14:19.560 --> 00:14:23.000
